data.enText: to sell and send goods to another country

data.chText: 这些岛屿出口糖和水果。
data.enText: The islands export sugar and fruit.
90% of the engines are exported to Europe.
to introduce an idea or activity to another country or area

data.chText: 美国流行音乐已传播到世界各地。
data.enText: American pop music has been exported around the world.
to send data to another program, changing its form so that the other program can read it
the selling and transporting of goods to another country
a ban on the export of live cattle
Then the fruit is packaged for export .
a product that is sold to another country
a fall in the value of exports

simple_means.memory_skill: ex 出，出去 + port 港口 →〔货物〕出港 → 出口

tr: commodities (goods or services) sold to a foreign country
cause to spread in another part of the world
example: The Russians exported Marxism to Africa

tr: transfer (electronic data) out of a database or document in a format that can be used by other programs

example: we export less than we import and have a negative trade balance

value.boxr_value: The verb is pronounced /ɪk'spɔːt/. The noun is pronounced /'ekspɔːt/. 动词读作 /ɪk'spɔːt/。名词读作 /'ekspɔːt/。

value.def: To export products or raw materials means to sell them to another country.

example.ex: They expect the antibiotic products to be exported to Southeast Asia and Africa...
example.tran: 他们希望向东南亚和非洲出口抗生素产品。

example.ex: To earn foreign exchange we must export.
example.tran: 要想获得外汇，我们必须出口。

example.ex: ...the production and export of cheap casual wear...
example.tran: 廉价休闲服装的生产和出口

example.ex: A lot of our land is used to grow crops for export.
example.tran: 我们有大片土地用来种植出口作物。

value.def: Exports are goods which are sold to another country and sent there.

example.ex: He did this to promote American exports...
example.tran: 他这么做是为了推广美国出口产品。
加纳的主要出口商品是可可豆。

value.def: To export something means to introduce it into another country or make it happen there.

example.ex: It has exported inflation at times.
example.tran: 它有时会输出通货膨胀。

example.ex: ...hecklers who said the deal would export jobs to Mexico.
example.tran: 声称这项协议会把就业机会转往墨西哥的质疑者

value.def: In computing, if you export files or information from one type of software into another type, you change their format so that they can be used in the new software.

example.ex: Files can be exported in ASCII or PCX formats.
example.tran: 文件可以以ASCII或者PCX格式导出。
